Interface JslipcBinman

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, Closeable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractChunkFileChannel, AbstractJslipcFileChannel, ChunkFilePipe, FilePipe, ReadableChunkFileChannel, ReadableJslipcFileChannel, SharedMemoryPipe, WritableChunkFileChannel, WritableJslipcFileChannel

    public interface JslipcBinman
extends Closeable
    If method cleanUpOnClose() is called prior to Closeable.close(), an implementation of this interface should try to release all resource it relies on (e.g. files, buffers, etc.), whether create by itself or passed in.
